<Title>Love My Dell, Dude!
<Date>Sun Dec 16 00:00:00 CST 2007
<Content>I love my Dell!  I've had it for a couple of years and it has only freezed on me once. And that was an easy fix.  I've yet to max out the 20 gig memory and when I first received it, it was easy plug and play.  I didn't have to read the manual to figure out how to work it.  Too bad Dell doesn't make these anymore.  I would totally recommend this player, even used!    
